item.title: rustdoc 范例
item.description: 1. rust doc /// A human being is represented here pub struct Person { /// A person must have a name, no matter how much Juliet may hate it name: String, } impl Person { /// Returns a person with the name given them /// /// # Arguments /// /// * `name` - A string slice that holds the name of the person /// /// # Example /// /// ``` /// // You can have rust code between fences inside the comments /// // If you pass --test to Rustdoc, it will even test it for you!
